lines.text: Don't worry baby, this my uncle's car, he lets me borrow it whenever I want.
OH YEAH! THEN WHY DID YOU HAVE TO HOT WIRE IT!

[as the gargantuan Finch tries to fit into a uniform]
Man, how'd your folks let you get like this?
Are you kidding? He probably ate his folks!

[after she runs the team into the ground, throws the broken watch on the ground]
You owe me a new stop watch... you PUSSIES!
Just remember; you can't win a pissing contest with a prick.
Get out of my face you fat fuck!
